<p>We all know that we're supposed to be saving money. It's no secret. But how much should we be saving? 15% of your income seems to be the generic advice, but the truth is that you have options far beyond any rule-of-thumb. Use those options to your advantage. Forget societal norms and instead let your personal goals guide you to the right answer.
